  "synopsis": "The \"Capsules Project\" invites professional teams from various industries with mature animation production experience to create short films ranging from 5 to 15 minutes, themed around \"Extreme Emotions.\" Teams will choose two of seven emotion capsules—\"Thorn,\" \"Desire,\" \"Joy,\" \"Illusion,\" \"Numbness,\" \"Tears,\" and \"Passion\"—and, based on their effects, create a collection of high-quality animated short films in different formats and styles. Through diverse forms and styles, the project aims to convey a variety of emotional stories and, together with Chinese animators, propel them onto the world stage.\n\n(Source: Bilibili, translated)",
